    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主线画出来：Client生成PKCE，重定向到Google OAuth，返回code，然后POST到AuthController。接下来GoogleOAuthService要去Google Token API换token对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
